text.section: Subsection (1)(a) of this section shall not apply to any entity not obligated to file an annual report.
Subsection (1)(b) and (c) of this section shall not apply to any entity that is not obligated to maintain a registered office and agent.

law.history: Created 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 151, sec. 35, effective January 1, 2011.
